<a name="_RefTop"></a>

<p>The login screen allows you to access the various types of
online play: Sierra Online, LAN, and Direct Connection.  Note that play on Sierra Online or via
Direct Connection requires an active Internet connection for your computer.</p>

<p>Please select the topic you would like help with:</p>

<ul type=square>
<li><a href=#_Ref10356744>Logging on to Sierra Online</a></li>

<li><a href=#_Ref10356796>Creating Sierra Online Accounts</a></li>

<li><a href=#_Ref10356800>Terms of Use Dialog</a></li>

<li><a href=#_Ref10356806>LAN and Direct Connection Play</a></li>

<li><a href=#_Ref10356824>Retrieving Lost Passwords</a></li>

<li><a href=#_Ref10356831>Retrieving Lost Usernames</a></li>

